WEBVTT

00:05.551 --> 00:07.386
<i>Previously on, "Rectify."</i>

00:07.387 --> 00:08.589
Where are you goin', Janet?

00:08.590 --> 00:10.555
Ted, we're not gonna
figure this out right now.

00:10.557 --> 00:11.991
Amantha and I are...

00:11.992 --> 00:13.993
<i>taking a step back for a bit,</i>

00:13.994 --> 00:15.094
<i>on a personal front.</i>

00:15.095 --> 00:17.230
<i>(JANET) Hey, Daniel. It's your mama.</i>

00:17.231 --> 00:19.298
<i>Everybody misses you terribly.</i>

00:19.299 --> 00:20.900
Well, I haven't been there for you.

00:20.901 --> 00:22.896
You've always been real
good to me, Janet.

00:22.897 --> 00:23.897
Oh, God.

00:23.898 --> 00:25.771
I wish I hadn't asked
you to call me Janet.

00:25.772 --> 00:27.173
What are you afraid of, Ted?

00:27.174 --> 00:28.841
I'm afraid I'm gonna lose her for good.

00:28.842 --> 00:31.043
I'd like to change the locks.

00:31.044 --> 00:33.961
Trey Willis, you're under arrest
for the murder of George Melton.

00:35.937 --> 00:40.609
(CREAKING, SCRAPING)

00:47.081 --> 00:49.141
(RATTLING)

00:50.051 --> 00:51.684
(FOOTSTEPS)

00:51.685 --> 00:53.920
(SIGHS)

00:53.921 --> 00:57.725
♪♪

00:59.793 --> 01:04.033
(RATTLING, SCRAPING)

01:07.635 --> 01:09.705
(FLOOR CREAKS)

01:13.741 --> 01:18.012
(RATTLING, SCRAPING)

01:18.013 --> 01:20.716
- TED JR.: Mornin'.
- TED SR.: Hey.

01:22.468 --> 01:23.836
(DOOR CLOSES)

01:25.287 --> 01:26.833
Wanta ride with me today?

01:26.835 --> 01:28.183
No, thanks.

01:28.184 --> 01:30.054
Got something going on tonight.

01:30.055 --> 01:31.441
That's good.

01:32.825 --> 01:34.828
Something interesting?

01:35.364 --> 01:36.824
I was gonna meet someone, Dad.

01:38.556 --> 01:40.626
Okay, cool.

01:43.135 --> 01:44.870
(SLURPING)

01:46.405 --> 01:48.140
(MUG THUDS)

01:51.977 --> 01:53.812
(DOOR CLOSES, KEYS JINGLE)

01:53.813 --> 01:55.714
All right. See you at work, I guess.

01:55.715 --> 01:57.741
Yeah, see ya in a few.

01:57.742 --> 01:59.643
(DOOR CLOSES)

01:59.644 --> 02:03.448
♪♪

